      <title>Are QA &amp; Test Engineers Safe in the Age of AI?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/qa-engineers-future-27-4-26/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 18:53:06 +0200</pubDate>
